22:33.309 --> 22:42.802
No, the Bible is primarily the story of God's salvation, of God's rescuing a wayward humanity through Jesus Christ.

22:43.714 --> 22:48.980
Whenever we open up the pages of Scripture, we are looking to find Jesus.

