23:13.186 --> 23:19.677
This is what God has done for us, giving us Jesus Christ, giving us his word that points to him.

23:20.859 --> 23:25.668
So scripture, understanding the Bible, it's calling out to God for understanding.

23:26.489 --> 23:28.553
