23:36.706 --> 23:53.142
allowing the scripture to read us, to look deep within us, to dissect us, coming before the scriptures laid bare, open, forgot to do his work, and looking to Jesus, allowing the scriptures to point us to Christ, the only one who grants us eternal life.

23:54.345 --> 23:56.690
All of God's people said, amen.

